We have become aware that if one does something and it is not visible from the outside, one’s own performance does not exist in a certain sense.
Thanks to EU funding, we can also afford good lecturers, high-quality equipment and more.
Was it your goal to get it this far with The Tap Tap?
From the beginning, I felt the potential to approach things differently.
In show business today, one often copies the other.
