It’s about giving readers a behind-the-scenes look, a look at who the 95 years of tension (calculated from the Balfour Declaration in November 1917) in the small patch of land in the Middle East above all serve.
My thoughts are partly based on accessible historical facts, others are derived from them and emerge from my own understanding of who or what group of people is influencing the events of modern history.
The history of mankind is primarily a history of the struggle for power.
